---
layout: base.njk
css:
  - /css/homepage.css
---
<section class="cb-hero">
  <div class="cb-top-section">
    <div class="cb-logo-circle">
      <div class="cb-logo-text">
          <p class="cb-brand">CareBridge</p>
          <p class="cb-motto">Healthcare for everyone</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="cb-message-box">
      <p class="cb-commitment">
        <span class="cb-highlight">Our Commitment:</span> 
        <span class="cb-underline">No one</span> should be denied treatment simply because they cannot afford it.
      </p>
      <blockquote class="cb-quote">
        “More than 1/2 the world’s population still can't get essential health services because they <strong>cannot afford</strong> it.”
        <cite>– WHO.int</cite>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="cb-button-group">
    <a href="/hospital-portal" class="cb-btn cb-btn-hospital">
        Be a CareBridge Partner
        <span class="cb-btn-sub">For Hospitals</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/login" class="cb-btn cb-btn-donor">
        Build the Bridge
        <span class="cb-btn-sub">For Donors</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/login" class="cb-btn cb-btn-patient">
        Get CareBridge Support
        <span class="cb-btn-sub">Register for Care</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="container" style="padding: 4rem 0;">
  <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem;">How CareBridge Works</h2>
  
  <div class="grid">
    <article style="text-align: center; border: none; background: var(--pico-card-background-color);">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 256 256" style="width: 56px; height: 56px;"><rect fill="none"/><line x1="24" y1="176" x2="232" y2="176" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="16"/><path d="M24,224S139.52,32,77.91,32C32.07,32,31.58,225.11,128,104.19c0,0,8.11,39.44,27.23,39.81,7.72.15,17.25-6.31,28.77-24,0,0,0,24,48,24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="16"/></svg>
      <h3>1. Verify</h3>
      <p>Hospitals and individuals upload verified medical bills and legal identification.</p>
    </article>

    <article style="text-align: center; border: none; background: var(--pico-card-background-color);">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 256 256" style="width: 56px; height: 56px;"><rect fill="none"/><circle cx="112" cy="112" r="80" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="16"/><line x1="168.57" y1="168.57" x2="224" y2="224" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="16"/></svg>
      <h3>2. Browse</h3>
      <p>Donors scroll through active requests and choose a cause that resonates with them.</p>
    </article>

    <article style="text-align: center; border: none; background: var(--pico-card-background-color);">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 256 256" style="width: 56px; height: 56px;"><rect fill="none"/><path d="M48,208H16a8,8,0,0,1-8-8V160a8,8,0,0,1,8-8H48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="16"/><path d="M112,160h32l67-15.41a16.61,16.61,0,0,1,21,16h0a16.59,16.59,0,0,1-9.18,14.85L184,192l-64,16H48V152l25-25a24,24,0,0,1,17-7H140a20,20,0,0,1,20,20h0a20,20,0,0,1-20,20Z" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="16"/><path d="M96.73,120C87,107.72,80,94.56,80,80c0-21.69,17.67-40,39.46-40A39.12,39.12,0,0,1,156,64a39.12,39.12,0,0,1,36.54-24C214.33,40,232,58.31,232,80c0,29.23-28.18,55.07-50.22,71.32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="16"/></svg>
      <h3>3. Impact</h3>
      <p>Direct payments clear the hospital debt instantly. No middlemen, no delays.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
<section id="home-impact-section" class="container-fluid" style="padding: 4rem 0;">
  <div class="container grid">
    <div>
      <img src="/icons/unsdg3.png" alt="UNSDG 3 Goal" style="border-radius: 8px; max-width: 300px;">
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2 style="color: white;">Aligning with UNSDG #3</h2>
      <p style="color: #bbb;">CareBridge is built to support <strong>Good Health and Well-being</strong>. By removing the financial barrier to essential medicine, we are helping to ensure healthy lives and promote well-being for all at all ages.</p>
      <ul style="color: #bbb;">
        <li>Reducing maternal mortality</li>
        <li>Ending preventable deaths</li>
        <li>Access to safe & affordable essential medicines</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="container" style="text-align: center; padding: 5rem 0;">
  <article style="padding: 3rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pico-primary) 0%, #2b5876 100%); color: white;">
    <h2 style="color: white;">Ready to bridge the gap?</h2>
    <p style="color: #ddd">Join hundreds of donors and hospitals working together to save lives.</p>
    <div class="grid" style="max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <a href="/signup" role="button" class="contrast">Start Donating</a>
      <a href="/signup-hospital" role="button" class="outline contrast" style="color: #ddd; border-color: currentColor">Register Hospital</a>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>
<footer class="container" style="padding: 2rem 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--pico-muted-border-color);">
  <div class="grid">
    <div>
      <p><strong>CareBridge</strong><br><small>© 2026. Built for the Health-Tech Hackathon.</small></p>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align: right;">
      <a href="/" class="secondary">Home</a> | 
      <a href="/about" class="secondary">About</a> | 
      <a href="/requests" class="secondary">Requests</a> | 
      <a href="/email-us" class="secondary">Contact</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
